# Styling and UI Rules

## Framework Stack
- **Tailwind CSS 3** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **Shadcn/ui** - Component library in `src/components/ui/`
- **Radix UI** - Accessible primitive components

## Design Patterns
- Mobile-first responsive design approach
- Dark/light theme support via CSS variables
- Flexbox layouts for component structure (see `Layout.tsx`)
- Consistent spacing and typography scale

## Best Practices
- Check `src/components/ui/` before creating new components
- To add new components execute the `npx shadcn@latest add <component>` command (e.g. `npx shadcn@latest add accordion`)
- Use semantic HTML with proper accessibility
- Leverage Tailwind's design tokens for consistency
- Implement proper focus states and keyboard navigation
